	<text xml:lang="la">
		<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" subtype="metadata" n="1">Der vorliegende Brief ist zweifelsfrei zwischen <ref target="file11793">Nr. 1747</ref> und 1754 einzureihen; vgl. unten Z. 1-5 mit Anm. 3-5.</note>
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quandoquidem non eum, quem putabam, nuncium<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Unbekannt.</note> nactus sum 24. maii<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Am 24. Mai hatte <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Blarer</persName> einen Brief an <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullinger</persName> geschrieben (oben <ref target="file11793">Nr. 1747</ref>).</note>, mitto partem libelli, quem <persName ref="p467" cert="high">Bucerus</persName> ędidit<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Gemeint ist offenbar <persName ref="p467" cert="high">Bucers</persName> Schrift "Was im namen des heiligen evangeli unsers herrenn Jesu Christi jetzund zu <placeName ref="l56" cert="high">Bonn</placeName> im stifft <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l267" cert="high">Cöllen</placeName> gelehret unnd geprediget würdt", Marburg (<persName ref="p4243" cert="high">Hermann Bastian</persName>) [<placeName ref="l56" cert="high">Bonn</placeName> (<persName ref="p18192" cert="high">Laurenz von der Mülen</persName>)] 1543 (BucerBibl 127), um deren Zusendung <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Blarer</persName> <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8385" cert="high">Konrad Hubert</persName> am 7. Mai gebeten hatte (<persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Blarer</persName> BW II, <ref target="file11049">Nr. 1007</ref>; Verdankung der Übersendung in <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Blarer</persName> BW II, <ref target="file11058">Nr. 1016</ref>).</note> quemque diebus hisce legere licuit<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a"><hi>Von</hi> quemque <hi>bis</hi> licuit <hi>am Rande nachgetragen.</hi></note>, posteriorem quoque, quę tribus quaternionibus hanc superat, missurus, ubi legero, tuque alteram hanc, quam nemo alius legit, remiseris<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5"><persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Blarer</persName> sandte <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullinger</persName> den zweiten Teil der Schrift am 15. Juni; vgl. unten <ref target="file11800">Nr. 1754</ref>, 15-20.</note>.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nullum hic est aliud exemplum, quinetiam <placeName ref="l491" cert="high">Argentorati</placeName> unum adhuc reliquum est.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Boni, puto, boni consulent hanc <persName ref="p467" cert="high">Buceri</persName> nostri doctrinam, praesertim ubi diligentius locum atque eos, quibuscum<note xml:id="fnb" type="footnote" n="b">cum <hi>über der Zeile nachgetragen.</hi></note> res<note xml:id="fnc" type="footnote" n="c"><hi>Vor</hi> res <hi>gestrichenes</hi> nunc.</note> illi nunc<note xml:id="fnd" type="footnote" n="d">nunc <hi>über der Zeile nachgetragen.</hi></note> est, expenderint; nam poterant alioqui nonnulla, quod nec <persName ref="p467" cert="high">Bucerus</persName> diffitebitur, luculentius et solidius tradi.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ipse vero de meipso coniecturam facio, quid, si hic essem, facerem.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus regni sui pomerio nostro ministerio magis atque magis proferat!</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">In quo, mi<note xml:id="fne" type="footnote" n="e"><hi>Vor</hi> mi <hi>gestrichenes q.</hi></note> venerande atque optime frater, bene et perpetuo vale.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Saluta fratres et amicos, cum primis <persName ref="p8011" cert="high">Gvaltherum</persName> nostrum.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="de" type="auto">30. maii 154[3]<note xml:id="fnf" type="footnote" n="f"><hi>Rand beschnitten.</hi></note>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambros. Blaurerus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">H. Bullingero</persName>, amice valde quam observande fratrique longe charissimo.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Zürich</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
